column2: SELECT TOP # chinook.Album.ArtistId, chinook.Track.AlbumId, count(*) as NUM_TRACKS, SUM(chinook.Track.UnitPrice) TotalPrice FROM chinook.Track INNER JOIN chinook.Album ON chinook.Track.AlbumId=chinook.Album.AlbumId GROUP BY chinook.Album.ArtistId GROUP BY chinook.Track.AlbumId ORDER BY TotalPrice DESC
